des:
Zorro Alert skill for Amazon Alexa products work together to help you control home appliance nice and easy.
You can simply ask Alexa to turn on or turn off the device.
There’s no need to go to the plug to adjust you home light - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, Amazon Tap or Echo Show.
After connecting Alexa to your Zorro Alert products in a few simple steps:
 (1). Download our " Zorro Smart" app in android or iOS app market.
 (2). Register one Zorro Smart account in our " Zorro Smart " app.
(3). You need to have some Zorro Alert devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our “Zorro Smart " app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in " Zorro Smart " skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android, iOS or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search " Zorro Smart" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of " Zorro Smart ", and you'll be navigated to Zorro Smart login page;
(9). Input your Zorro Smart account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.

You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on kitchen plug"
“Alexa, turn off kitchen plug"
Currently this skill supports products:
smart plug
